      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014it basically looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s been parked in a garage its whole life. Not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives so smoothly, you\u2019ve really gotta see it for yourself to believe it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! Come take a look and fall in love!",
