    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double VANOS system. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with a recent rod bearing service and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The chassis dynamics are enhanced by a factory limited-slip differential and a perfectly damped suspension that retains original geometry. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, mechanical throws with zero synchro hesitation. Every surface, from the pristine undercarriage to the Nappa leather interior, reflects a rigorous maintenance schedule and climate-controlled preservation. This is a turnkey performance icon for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
